               stealing, of the <rs id="t18280703-34-cd181" type="crimeDate">9th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280703-34-off180 t18280703-34-cd181"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280703-34-victim345" type="victimName">
                        James 
                        Palmer
                     <interp inst="t18280703-34-victim345" type="surname" value="Palmer"></interp>
